  "3094970": {
    "name": "Spires of Morosith: Gossamer Sundered",
    "steam_appid": 3094970,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《莫罗西斯之塔》是一款结合了即时战略元素的战术塔防游戏。《莫罗斯之塔》允许玩家掌控战场地形与敌军行进路线，致力于深化周围环境对经典塔防玩法的影响。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >⠀</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3094970/extras/d805b08231d138a5ee46611d37b9f35b.avif?t=1763148770\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3094970/extras_big/d805b08231d138a5ee46611d37b9f35b.avif?t=1763148770 width=800 height=222 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>入侵的谷灵</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >谷灵正通过裂隙撕裂树谷镇。它们企图摧毁生成灵网的尖塔，不吞噬整个树谷镇誓不罢休。</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >谷灵种类繁多，既有数量众多的小型侦察兵，也有罕见而骇人的畸变体。</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >敌人可能以特殊形态出现。例如，吸引塔楼火力以保护身旁小型谷灵的巨象，或在死亡时制造小型裂隙，从而滋生更多敌人的特洛伊。</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >首领波次将考验你的战略部署，并且会对你的防守薄弱环节出招。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >⠀</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3094970/extras/34a965bcb90ef908bf1a7c49c069719f.avif?t=1763148770\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3094970/extras_big/34a965bcb90ef908bf1a7c49c069719f.avif?t=1763148770 width=800 height=222 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>召唤防御塔</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >从五种防御塔中召唤部署，每种塔都有独特功能，可用于击退入侵的谷灵。</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每座塔拥有一至两条升级路线，可进一步突显其独特机制，有时还会附加燃烧、易伤或减速等额外效果。</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >召唤防御塔会影响谷灵到达尖塔的路径。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >⠀</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3094970/extras/482cb65bae8a7318832b4111ebd761e6.avif?t=1763148770\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3094970/extras_big/482cb65bae8a7318832b4111ebd761e6.avif?t=1763148770 width=800 height=222 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>辅助建筑</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过建造建筑提升资源生成与采集效率。</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >建筑不会对谷灵造成伤害，但在保护树谷镇及尖塔方面，具有与防御塔同样重要的作用。</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >建筑会影响谷灵路线，且占地面积（2x2）大于防御塔（1x1）。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >⠀</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3094970/extras/5e23c2aa9f694d4b62fb2b3f35071472.avif?t=1763148770\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3094970/extras_big/5e23c2aa9f694d4b62fb2b3f35071472.avif?t=1763148770 width=800 height=222 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>莫罗斯之塔与方尖碑</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >活跃的尖塔形成灵网屏障，阻止谷灵入侵树谷镇。将其禁用后，谷灵就会试图摧毁它们。</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >保护尖塔是首要任务。谷灵到达尖塔时会造成重大伤害。</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >生存并不等于胜利。必须重新激活树谷镇的尖塔以修复灵网，阻止谷灵通过裂隙入侵。</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一旦方尖碑收集到足够的谷灵核心，它们就有可能为附近的尖塔提供能量。击败方尖碑区域内的谷灵以收集其核心！</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >⠀</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3094970/extras/e0bde9ce2c28c3c86c66ba4ac6dbfdb7.avif?t=1763148770\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3094970/extras_big/e0bde9ce2c28c3c86c66ba4ac6dbfdb7.avif?t=1763148770 width=800 height=222 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>采集者西蒙和艾伦</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >可以指挥采集者在地图上收集资源。请谨慎采集，资源一旦收集便会从地图上消失！</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >移除资源能为防御塔腾出更多空间，但也可能为谷灵开辟通往尖塔的新路线！</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >采集者还可能在树谷镇的森林中发现远古知识，为你的军械库增添新的防御塔与建筑！</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>树谷镇</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >树谷镇的三大区域为你提供了拓展防御战略的广阔空间。</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >如何让防御体系融入茂密的森林？如何掌控浮空岛的传送连接和有限的路径？是否有足够的时间清除枯树根以到达心木树林？</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >建造时需注意区域内的野生生物，它们可能会试图保护自己的领地！</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>ADDITIONAL FEATURES</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >遇到棘手的谜题时，推演结果能帮助你克服前方的障碍。《莫罗西斯之塔》为追求清晰战术的玩家提供了以下辅助功能：</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每成功抵御一波进攻都会生成战报，显示该波次获取的核心数量与尖塔受损的情况。</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >将鼠标悬停在木材库存与波次显示器上，可查看每分钟资源生成量与波次难度数据。</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你可以在暂停期间规划防御塔蓝图——它会临时更新谷灵路径。这有助于你设计精妙的迷宫阵型。</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你可以在感觉时机成熟的情况下，尝试挑战无尽模式，看看尖塔在永无止境的谷灵狂潮中究竟能坚守多久。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
